## Required Context Files

**Lost or unsure what to do?** Read the framework START_HERE files (referenced via `opencode.json` instructions list).

**Free-text entry points:** If you don't know which skill to run, invoke `@x-director - <describe what you want>`. x-director resolves all three frameworks from the paths below.

## Framework paths (external to this repo)

The three Agent OS frameworks are **not** nested inside this repository. They are referenced via absolute paths configured in `opencode.json` and available at:

| Framework | Path | Director |
|-----------|------|----------|
| Agent OS (`.ai`) | `/mnt/work/Projects/.ai` | `@ai-director` |
| UI Design OS (`.ai.ui`) | `/mnt/work/Projects/.ai.ui` | `@ui-director` |
| Business OS (`.ai.biz`) | `/mnt/work/Projects/.ai.biz` | `@biz-director` |

### Path resolution

x-director and ai-director resolve frameworks using the `opencode.json` references. Preflight check before routing: verify the framework's `skills/README.md` exists at the declared path.

Read these at the start of every conversation and when relevant:

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| **`opencode.json`** (repo root) | Framework registry, skill paths, instructions |
| **`DOCS_TECH_STACK.md`** | Technology stack |
| **`.work/context/HANDOFF.md`** | Session handoff |
| **`.work/plans/NEXT.md`** | Active iteration, recommended next |
| **`.ai/START_HERE.md`** via `/mnt/work/Projects/.ai/START_HERE.md` | Agent OS operator tree |
| **`.ai.ui/START_HERE.md`** via `/mnt/work/Projects/.ai.ui/START_HERE.md` | UI operator tree |
| **`.ai.biz/START_HERE.md`** via `/mnt/work/Projects/.ai.biz/START_HERE.md` | Business operator tree |

