## Skills

Reusable agent skills live under the framework skill paths. Available skills are registered in each framework's `skills/README.md`.

**Usage:** When a task matches a skill's purpose, read `skill.md` and follow the workflow. Skills are tool-agnostic (Cursor, Claude Code, Codex, opencode, etc.).

